{
  "text": "Briefly, the incidence calculation was performed following the recommendations of Surveillance and Survey and the Laboratory Working Groups (2006) . The guide's recommended adjustment factors for the sensitivity and specificity of the test were applied to estimate the incidence and conduct surveillance using the BED-CEIA. The unadjusted BED-CEIA incidence and two adjusted corrections with 95% CIs were estimated [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
